OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud will
OL,6,Fthicken this evening with the odd spot
OL,7,Fof light rain possible near western
OL,8,Fcoasts, but otherwise it will remain
OL,9,Fdry. Southerly coastal winds initially
OL,10,Ffresh.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FEastern coastal areas
OL,13,Fmilder than Tuesday. Elsewhere
OL,14,Fsignificantly cooler. Rather cloudy
OL,15,Fmorning with some patchy light rain,
OL,16,Fmostly confined to the west. Mainly
OL,17,Fdry for afternoon with brighter spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
