OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,6,Fearly Thursday, clearing to brighter
OL,7,Fspells and showers for afternoon.
OL,8,FFriday wet and windy with best of
OL,9,Fshelter in east. Blustery showers
OL,10,FSaturday, heavier and more frequent in
OL,11,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
